title: 8 AM Hour - Nolan Chooses The Love of His Life
description:
Falen is officially in Spain and looks like she's having a lot of fun! Dave is back on the show today!

We brought Nolan to the show who had a viral TikTok about finding someone to take to weddings this summer and he choose his date for this summer, & More!
